quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  26,123,Aad (ummanni huud) ergamtoota sobsiifte
  26,124,"Yeroo obboleessi isaanii Huud isaaniin jedhe: “Sila (Rabbiin) hin sodaattanii"
  26,125,Ani isiniif ergamaa amanamaadha
  26,126,Rabbiin sodaadhaa; ajaja kiyyas fudhaa
  26,127,Ani isa (waamicha kana) irratti mindaa tokkollee isin hin gaafadhu; mindaan kiyya Gooftaa aalama hundaa irratti malee hin taane
  26,128,"Sila isin kan [nama tarutti] qishintanu taatanii iddoo ol fuudhamaa hunda irratti [gamoo] mallattoo ijaartuu"
  26,129,Kuusaa bishaaniitiifi gamoowwanis akka waan keessatti haftanuutti tolfattuu
  26,130,"Yeroo [namoota adabbiif] qabdanis gara jabeeyyii taatanii qabdan"
  26,131,Rabbiin sodaadhaa; ajaja kiyyas fudhaa
  26,132,"Isa waan [gaggaarii] isin beektan hundaan isin badhaases sodaadhaa"
  26,133,Beyladootaafi ilmaaniinis isin badhaase
  26,134,"Ashaakiltiiwwaniifi burqaawwaniinis [isin qananiise]"
  26,135,Ani adabbii Guyyaa guddaan isin irratti sodaadha.”
  26,136,"[Ummanni Huud] ni jedhan: “Yoo nu gorsites yoo warra gorsan irraa ta’uu baattes nurratti waluma qixa"
  26,137,Kun amaluma warra duriiti malee waan biraa miti
  26,138,"Nuti kan adabamnuu miti” [jedhan]"
  26,139,"Isa sobsiisanii Nutis isaan balleessineDhugumatti, kana keessa mallattootu jiraGaruu irra hedduun isaanii mu’uminoota hin taane"
  26,140,"Dhugumatti, Rabbiin kee Isatu injifataa, rahmata godhaadha"